&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1981 malayalam disaster drama film , written and directed by p. n. sundaram , and starring jayan . the film was a box office hit . on 16 november 1980 , jayan was killed in an accident on the set of &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the climax scene of the film was being filmed in &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , near chennai , tamil nadu . jayan performed an own stunt that involved him boarding an airborne helicopter from a moving motorbike . jayan insisted on another take as he was not satisfied . during the take , the pilot lost control and crashed the helicopter while jayan was hanging below leading to his death .